text: Vaceuchelus pagoboorum is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Chilodontidae. ==Description== The size of the shell varies between 4.7 mm and 7.5 mm. ==Distribution== This marine species occurs off the Philippines. ==References== ==External links== * pagoboorum Category:Gastropods described in 2006
title: Vaceuchelus pagoboorum
